            <td><span style=" font-family:'宋体'; color:#F60">*</span>
              <input id="Email" name="Email" type="text" class="textInput" onBlur="checkEmail();"/></td>
            <td><div id="EmailNote" class="gray">您的邮箱是找回密码的重要途径，请您仔细填写。</div></td>
          </tr>
